# Deployment & Feeds

- Default deployment target is Vercel per [`vercel.json`](mdc:vercel.json).
- Containerization supported with [`Dockerfile`](mdc:Dockerfile) and [`Dockerfile.dev`](mdc:Dockerfile.dev); orchestration via [`K8s.yaml`](mdc:K8s.yaml).
- Static feeds (`rss.xml`, `atom.xml`, `sitemap.xml`) reside in `public/`. Scripts to generate them: [`gen-rss.js`](mdc:scripts/gen-rss.js), [`gen-atom.js`](mdc:scripts/gen-atom.js), [`gen-sitemap.js`](mdc:scripts/gen-sitemap.js).
- Automate feed generation in CI before deploy to avoid committing generated artifacts.
